         <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">Ernest R. Olson, Jr. worked for the Interstate Commerce Commission as Associate Director in the Office of Policy and Analysis and as Assistant Director of Traffic.  The collection contains a variety of materials pertaining to railroads beyond the New England area.</abstract>
