      <bioghist altrender="biography" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
         <head>Biography</head>
         <p>
            <persname>Ernest R. Olson, Jr.</persname> worked for the <corpname>Interstate Commerce Commission</corpname> as Associate Director in the Office of Policy and Analysis and as Assistant Director of Traffic.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>The collection includes broadsides, reports, correspondence and memoranda concerning railroads beyond the New England area.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <relatedmaterial encodinganalog="544 1" id="a6">
         <head>Related Material</head>
         <p>Archives &#x0026; Special Collections has a substantial collection of collections pertaining to New England railroads.  For detailed information on these collections please contact the <extref href="http://doddcenter.uconn.edu/asc/dodda2z/curatorinfo.cfm?curatorinfo=4">curator</extref> or ask at the reference desk.</p>
      </relatedmaterial>
